852
00:44:25,820 --> 00:44:27,540
When I went home this time,

853
00:44:28,220 --> 00:44:30,700
I realized my parents had changed too.

854
00:44:30,700 --> 00:44:31,700
They've aged.

855
00:44:32,220 --> 00:44:34,700
They're no longer invincible.

856
00:44:35,180 --> 00:44:36,140
Do you know?

857
00:44:36,220 --> 00:44:38,260
